_sText:
The map has 64 spawn points, radar view, soundscapes and two bombsites. Server tested on css1.astramania.ro , excelent fps.

Special thanks to Wicked ,the owner of Astramania servers and to Astramania community for testing and playing my maps.

To HDR lovers: due to a couple of textures from cs_office i could not use HDR lightning because after building the cubemaps,those textures looked annoyingly bright and shiny.
Don't be upset, you have more fps now!
